results.name: Womens 1996 Retro Nuptse 700 Fill Packable
results.title: The North Face Womens 1996 Retro Nuptse 700 Fill Packable Jacket Recycled TNF Black
results.description:
The North Face Womens 1996 Retro Nuptse 700 Fill Packable Jacket Recycled TNF Black, appearing in all sizes for women, is a garment that in a dark color.

This 1996 Retro Nuptse 700 jacket by The North Face features secure-zip hand pockets, a shockcord at the hem, non-PFC DWR finish for water repellency, an encased-elastic cuffs featuring adjustable hook-and-loop cuff tabs, and Triclimate loops for snap-in compatibility.

The The North Face Womens 1996 Retro Nuptse 700 Fill Packable Jacket Recycled TNF Black retailed for $132 at the time of its debut on the 23rd of July, 2022.

results.name: x NOCTA Women's Chalet Polar
results.title: Nike x NOCTA Women's Chalet Polar Top Dark Blue
results.description:
Since first launching his Nike sub-line, NOCTA, in 2020, Drake has churned out a variety of hoodies for both men and women. The Nike x NOCTA Women's Chalet Polar Top Dark Blue was a women's-exclusive hoodie that featured a relatively straightforward design with several touches that helped separate it from other hoodies that Nike and NOCTA have released in the past.

This navy blue hoodie was made of 100% polyester, and it also boasted a 100% cotton lining. It had a large kangaroo pouch on the front of it, along with a pocket on the back that came with a magnetic zipper. An elastic binding at both the hem and the cuff tied the appearance of the hoodie together and emphasized its loose fit.

Although this hoodie didn't push too many boundaries in terms of its design, our experts appreciated its simplicity and the small details that differentiated it from the pack. The Nike x NOCTA Women's Chalet Polar Top Dark Blue was first released on December 6, 2023, and it retailed for $120.

results.name: x Travis Scott Cactus Jack Women's Leather
results.title: Jordan x Travis Scott Cactus Jack Women's Leather Jacket Archaeo Brown
results.description:
The Jordan x Travis Scott Cactus Jack Women's Leather Jacket Archaeo Brown is a collaboration between Jordan and Travis Scott. It is made of brown leather and features Cactus Jack branding on the front and back.

This Jordan x Travis Scott Cactus Jack leather jacket is crafted from premium materials, ensuring both durability and style. It is made of brown leather, exuding a sense of timeless elegance. It also features a satin lining, and comes in various sizes. The jacket’s other great features include a snap closure collar, full-length zip, Cactus Jack logo embroidery, and Air Jordan patches. It also has a removable hood and zippered pockets. The design features intricate detailing, showcasing a unique blend of streetwear and luxury fashion, a hallmark of Travis Scott’s creative influence and love of vintage clothing.

What our experts love about this jacket is the intricate detailing. The leather is soft and supple, and also the stitching.. The patches and embroidery are also high-quality and add a touch of luxury. The Jordan x Travis Scott Cactus Jack Women's Leather Jacket Archaeo Brown was released on April 26th, 2023 and retailed for $600.

results.name: Women's Letter Graphic Cotton Blend Zip
results.title: Burberry Women's Letter Graphic Cotton Blend Zip Hoodie Black
results.description:
Burberry is a brand that has been around for almost 170 years, so the company has certainly created its fair share of hoodies at this point. But the Burberry Women's Letter Graphic Cotton Blend Zip Hoodie Black seemed to be proof that it isn't going to stop coming up with new hoodie designs anytime soon.

This particular hoodie featured a regular fit, a zip-up closure, and a relatively basic design that allowed the Burberry check pattern to shine. The bulk of the hoodie was done up in black, aside from the gold zipper and, of course, the Burberry check pattern that appeared prominently on the interior of its hood.

What we loved most about this hoodie was the simplicity of it all. Rather than going with a more over-the-top design, Burberry chose to stick with what has worked for the brand in the past by letting its signature check pattern do the talking. The Burberry Women's Letter Graphic Cotton Blend Zip Hoodie Black was released as part of Burberry's Spring/Summer 2023 collection and originally retailed for $920.

results.name: x NOCTA Women's Chalet Polar
results.title: Nike x NOCTA Women's Chalet Polar Pant Dark Blue
results.description:
The Nike x NOCTA Women's Chalet Polar Pant Dark Blue is a collaborative piece between Nike and NOCTA, a sub-label founded by Canadian rapper Drake. Designed with comfort and style in mind, these pants offer a blend of athletic functionality and urban streetwear aesthetics.

Crafted from soft, high-quality polar fleece fabric, these pants feature a relaxed, straight-leg silhouette with a slightly tapered hem for a modern look. Their predominant color is dark blue, offering a versatile and timeless aesthetic. Its elastic waistband provides a secure and adjustable fit, while the drawstring closure allows for further customization when it comes to sizing.

What our experts especially enjoy about the Nike x NOCTA Womens Chalet Polar Pant Dark Blue, however, is the subtle white NOCTO and Nike branding on the legs. These pants originally retailed for a price of $110 when they were released on December 6, 2023.

results.title: Nike Womens Oversized Swoosh Logo Jacket Black/Fossil
results.description:
The Nike Womens Oversized Swoosh Logo Jacket Black Fossil became available as part of a women's collection by apparel and manufacturer brand Nike.

The Oversized Swoosh Logo Jacket comes in black and fossil and is made using faux fur and polyester materials. This sherpa fleece garment displays side pockets, an elastic hem, cuffs, and a collar. In addition, it has a full zipper at the front and a large white Nike logo done in white color running across the chest, which gives it its overall look.

The Nike Womens Oversized Swoosh Logo Jacket Black Fossil was released on the 1st of February 2022 and retailed for $170.
